  <official_title>Limb Injuries and Post Injury Rehabilitation Trials - Tibial Shaft Fracture (LIMPER-TSF): a Protocol for Prospective, Randomized,Multicentre Trial Comparing the Early Partial and Early Full Weightbearing After Nailed Tibial Shaft Fracture</official_title>
